latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Happy friendship day to my best friend, my sister, my love, my everything ❤️
We have been through thick and thin in our friendship.. but still chose to stay beside each other for 10 YEARS now❤️
I apologize for all my mistakes 🙏 
I love you with all my heart❤️ @shre.yya_

latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy Birthday Love❤️ @_rashmirekha_1111
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
You know i am weak at expressing my feelings, especially to you.. but just a few things which i don't think I'd be able to say you face to face..
You are my support, my advisor, my guide, my friend, my sister, my flatmate, my only hope to survive in pune❤️ without you, life wouldn't have been the same, i believe it's you who made me experience and come out of the small world i was living in.. it's you who made me believe in myself.. it's you who heard all my rants and still be patient with me everytime, it's you who cried if i did something stupid😂 ( i hope you get it).. it's you who managed with such a messy and a stupid flatmate 😛.. it's you and only you who could handle me once i am drunk.. it's you who slept beside me at night when i was in my toughest phase of life.. 
i can really go on and on.. but.. i just want to tell you, thank you for everything you ever did for me and i love you with all my heart❤️ 
Happy 21st birthday babe.🌍
p.s. i wish we could celebrate your birthday with a hell lot of blast, but surely once we are back in pune.. we're gonna rock it😛

latestIgtvVideos.title: #winners🤩 #magicbrushchallenge💄 #patriotictheme🇮🇳
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We participated in JITO's ( Jain International Trade Organization ) 'magic brush challenge'.
From more than 200 group entries, my team stood in top 10 for the finale round.🤩💃 Our theme was 'Indian Brides and their cultural dance forms'
You can have a look at the 1st round video @makeupbysurbhik in her account.

For the second round we were given the theme as patriotic. WE STOOD 3RD IN THE FINALE ROUND🤩❤️
Here's the video of our entry in the finale round😍 with my girls @shre.yya_ @thehushgirl_ @surbhijain13 @new_shah_ @jainashi59
